ery deed of the son of Adam is for him, except for fasting. It is for Me and I will reward it.\u2019 Fasting is a shield, so when one of you fasts, he may\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15275,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/invitation-dua-for-host\/","url_meta":{"origin":3785,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Invitations: Accept invites, supplicate for host","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf one of you is invited for a meal, let him respond. If he is fasting, let him pray for the host. If he is not fasting, let him eat.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1431 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5250,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/17\/fasting-ramadan-six-shawwal\/","url_meta":{"origin":3785,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Recommendation to fast six days of Shawwal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts the month of Ramadan and then follows it with six days of fasting in the month of Shawwal, it will be as if he has fasted for the entire year.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1164\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3761,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/23\/prophet-observed-wasala-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":3785,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: The Prophet continuously fasted, Muslims may not","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would observe continuous fasting during the month of Ramadan and so did the people, but he prohibited them. It was said, \u201cYou are continuously fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I am not like you, for I am\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/31\/fasting-ashura-9th-muharram\/","url_meta":{"origin":3785,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ashura: Fasting day of &#8216;Ashura with 9th of Muharram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 31, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hakam ibn al-A\u2019raj reported: I went to Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and I said, \u201cTell me about fasting the day of 'Ashura.\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cWhen you see the crescent of the month of al-Muharram, count the days and wake up to fast on the ninth\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadith